Enron Auction London UKAuctionsAuctionDetailaspauctionID Story from below Roll up for the Enron auction webcast By John Lettice Posted at EST Seeing everybody else has been doing the Enron auction and all the shredder jokes we werent going to bother but our eye couldnt help catching the featured items in the London sale and it all became somehow entrancing The shredders BBC Radio tells us this morning have been withdrawn but Cisco routers and switches Who cares Compaq and Sun servers maybe more interesting and and in flat panel displays Yum We cant be bothered digging into the catalogue to see if the workstations are proper ones or just more Compaqs but then the list gets seriously weird Fully equipped Techno Gym Contents of Cafe and Pitstops Pitstops Wassat Contents of laundy eeugh Meeting Rooms people people Theyre auctioning people Modern Artworks Hurry hurry folks it commences at am GMT today through Friday and if you cant get yourself to London SW youll find details of the webcast here Jim Lokay Questcom
